{"tid":913727,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"350萬人冒寒觀賞紐約感恩節巡遊 巨型龍珠氣球搶鏡","createTime":"2018-11-23T15:32:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T06:37:13.000Z","uid":179810,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e6ef4ba6bf429a2a32df24e7241e21e501cf58ac","tid":913727,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T15:32:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.cnbetacdn.com/article/2018/1123/0ffa6a1f2e13632.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.cnbetacdn.com%2Farticle%2F2018%2F1123%2F0ffa6a1f2e13632.jpg&h=ece6f245&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一年一度的感恩節巡遊周四在紐約市登場，數以百萬計民眾不畏攝氏零下6度低溫，夾道歡迎花車、巨型氣球與藝人演出，為紐約市百年來最冷的感恩節增添暖意。<br />\n<br />\n美國國家氣象局表示，今天是紐約市自1901年以來最冷的感恩節。由於紐約市官方事先發出極寒天氣警告，民眾都做足準備，除了禦寒必備的大衣、帽子、圍巾和手套，還有人裹著棉被和睡袋在路邊欣賞巡遊。<br />\n<br />\n感恩節巡遊今年踏入第92屆，巡遊路線維持傳統，從中央公園西側往南遊行到梅西百貨公司旗艦店，橫跨46個街區，總長約4公里。主辦單位估計，沿途吸引多達350萬人到場湊熱鬧。<br />\n<br />\n巨型氣球一向是梅西百貨感恩節遊行最大賣點，動畫《龍珠超》（Dragon Ball Super）主角悟空氣球首次加入遊行陣容，5層樓高的尺寸在16個巨型角色氣球中名列前茅，需要90人在地面牽著繫繩前進。另一人氣鼎盛的巨型氣球是海綿寶寶。這個動畫角色近20年前誕生，今年是第13次參加巡遊，所經之處民眾不分老少高喊「海綿寶寶」，足見人氣歷久不衰。比卡超、麥當勞叔叔、查理布朗、動畫《魔雪奇緣》（Frozen）角色雪寶等汽球亦大受歡迎。Diana Ross及芝麻街的布公仔亦在場演出助興。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/3/2018/11/23/9/9b69415fa305f54fe1302b94c3175ffc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F3%2F2018%2F11%2F23%2F9%2F9b69415fa305f54fe1302b94c3175ffc.jpg&h=1e6d3440&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據主辦方介紹，悟空氣球有56英呎高，寬達7輛出租車的長度。而在遊行前，主辦方也在Twitter上發表了一篇關於氣球設計的推文，說明了該氣球是有Toei Animation公司製造的<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/3/2018/11/23/8/813d0fe2797c63b841359bdd156aaa4f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F3%2F2018%2F11%2F23%2F8%2F813d0fe2797c63b841359bdd156aaa4f.jpg&h=79f9a1e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n悟空將是歷史上首位參加感恩節大遊行的日本漫畫人物，而在推特上我們還看到了隊伍中巨型比卡超的身姿。這是否標誌著在接下來的感恩節大遊行中，會有其他獨立於美國文化外的吉祥物出現呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/3/2018/11/23/9/949d70e204240b90e743e61577c9ac0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F3%2F2018%2F11%2F23%2F9%2F949d70e204240b90e743e61577c9ac0c.jpg&h=e7f16a73&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7f02563e13c52d3c237dd149c2770dca319c3fa","tid":913727,"uid":66436,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T15:37:40.000Z","msg":"還有人裹著棉被和睡袋在路邊欣賞巡遊。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be7bd32f9d0d76c1ac06886912970390f0870c4c","tid":913727,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T16:15:46.000Z","msg":"全部日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34874a9251252ff70ed207f000f6a47db6fd1d6f","tid":913727,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7f02563e13c52d3c237dd149c2770dca319c3fa","tid":913727,"uid":66436,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T15:37:40.000Z","msg":"還有人裹著棉被和睡袋在路邊欣賞巡遊。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T16:16:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"765a277308497bad38011c65157ce496f88516d6","tid":913727,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7f02563e13c52d3c237dd149c2770dca319c3fa","tid":913727,"uid":66436,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T15:37:40.000Z","msg":"還有人裹著棉被和睡袋在路邊欣賞巡遊。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T16:21:04.000Z","msg":"thanksgiving = 美國冬至"},{"pid":"3306c84ac688a20ceb4aacb4e784e9f9f507f084","tid":913727,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7f02563e13c52d3c237dd149c2770dca319c3fa","tid":913727,"uid":66436,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T15:37:40.000Z","msg":"還有人裹著棉被和睡袋在路邊欣賞巡遊。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"r